Diagram 1 (Matbogi)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's wedge at B1 is creative but hasty.
\par
\par White can answer simplly at 2 and leave black with no follow up moves.
\par
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj Now, \b\f1 A\b0\f0  and \b\f1 B\b0\f0  are matbogi for live and the white group lives easily.
\par }
